{"tid":1491323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"藍絲諗住824圍港台","createTime":"2019-08-20T11:28:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T01:00:51.000Z","uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a0c6c964d2401f35e5fd4c7261b624a60d4a71fe","tid":1491323,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:28:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FMpV2YV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFMpV2YV.jpg&h=839b30b0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uDYDgiW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuDYDgiW.jpg&h=1d1d4a14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由於出席人數可能極多 有部分朋友不知道路線 我們相約2點在樂富站集合 2點15分一起上香港電台 香港政研會將會有義工在旁協助<br />\n<br />\n今次又幾多慢人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e65da8acd9e9ff12ccf8a29c879cbc091f36f0f","tid":1491323,"uid":9328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:28:55.000Z","msg":"非法集結"},{"pid":"54d83e2fc89122cefc9a8fffbf1421f93bb31024","tid":1491323,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:30:53.000Z","msg":"藍絲諗住將琴日單野講成自編自導自演<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e8J7T6B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe8J7T6B.png&h=204e3834&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b7973fb4cec8ee844a77d48c8194a1a8783f859a","tid":1491323,"uid":160147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:33:52.000Z","msg":"香港政研會？ <br />\n即係邊個出錢遊行？"},{"pid":"38eca87663f5e9ebf21bcf2a3edda65fa232e892","tid":1491323,"uid":279616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:37:37.000Z","msg":"膠都費事派，等睇去錯廣播道3號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重申七一宣言，設立死線，立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n「勇武派」、「和理非」係角色，唔係派系，理念一致，只係手法不同<br />\n<br />\n唔係仇警，大家一定要清楚知道點解要清算警隊。警暴（濫捕、濫告、不依法規）係暴政一部分，唔全面改革警隊、監警制度，只會令目前同將來爭取雙普選更加舉步維艱<br />\n<br />\n所以，絕對唔需要否認自己係針對警隊，針對警隊就係對準政權。唔通你淨係針對林鄭、唔針對政制，就會有雙普選？<br />\n<br />\n#五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n#唔撤就罷<br />\n#罷工罷巿罷買罷課<br />\n#我係香港人<br />\n#我參與全港四罷<br />\n#各區集會<br />\n#出核彈麻包袋都唔割蓆<br />\n#直至政府跪低<br />\n#重組警隊 改革監警制度<br />\n#永遠不光顧荃灣北角元朗商戶<br />\n#抵制一切紅媒相關商業活動"},{"pid":"356bf74503a544cd8ce9e96ffe5034b52839fb26","tid":1491323,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:00:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n女義士被凌辱<br />\n新屋嶺集中營<br />\n五大訴求全無<br />\n爆眼護士之仇<br />\n元朗警黑合作<br />\n航空業大清算<br />\n被捕者七百餘<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n乜仇都未報到，唔好擺低你既憤怒！<br />\n我地絕對唔可以習慣，手足們繼續上街抗爭<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">８２４上午和你塞，下午觀塘遊行<br />\n８２５荃葵青大遊行</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uwUfM2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuwUfM2a.jpg&h=978ea62a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}